Veteran Nollywood Actress, Patience Oseni is dead. Her death was confirmed by the National President of AGN, Ejezie Emeka Rollas in a statement Patience Oseni said: “With deep sense of sorrow but with total submission to the will of Almighty God, we announce the passing unto eternal glory of Patience Oseni, veteran Actress and member of the Actors Guild of Nigeria.” Hit-and-run lorry driver kills 1 on River Niger Bridge – FRSC Oseni before her death was a member of the Actors Guild of Nigeria (AGN) The deceased started her acting career when she first starred in the movie ‘Deadly Passion.’ in 1995 Oseni rose to prominence in Nollywood back in the late 1990s with her role in the movie ‘End Of The Wicked.’ and Super story series ‘heat of the moment’